<lb n="0507b08" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0507b09" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 116 [Nos. 99(1073), 100(12), 117,
<lb n="0507b10" ed="T"/>125(23.5)]</cb:docNumber><cb:div type="jing">
<lb n="0507b11" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><title>佛說戒德香經</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0507b12" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0507b13" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">東晉天竺三藏竺曇無蘭譯</byline>
<lb n="0507b14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT02p0507b1401">聞如是：</p><p xml:id="pT02p0507b1404" rend="inline">一時，佛遊舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。時，
<lb n="0507b15" ed="T"/>賢者阿難閑居獨思：「世有三香，一曰根香，
<lb n="0507b16" ed="T"/>二曰枝香，三曰華香，是三品香唯隨風香不
<lb n="0507b17" ed="T"/>能逆風，寧有雅香隨風逆風者乎？」賢者阿難
<lb n="0507b18" ed="T"/>獨處思惟<app><lem wit="【CBETA】【麗】" resp="CBETA.maha">此<note type="cf1">K19n0713_p0613a08</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">於</rdg></app>義所歸，不知所趣，即從坐起往
<lb n="0507b19" ed="T"/>詣佛所，稽首<note n="0507008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛〕－【三】</note><note n="0507008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507008"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>足下，<note n="0507009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔長跪叉手〕－【三】</note><note n="0507009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔長跪叉手〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507009"><lem wit="【大】">長跪叉手</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="0507010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">而＝前【三】</note><note n="0507010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">而＝前【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507010"><lem wit="【大】">而</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">前</rdg></app>白佛言：
<lb n="0507b20" ed="T"/>「我獨處思惟，世有三香，一曰根香，二曰枝香，
<lb n="0507b21" ed="T"/>三曰華香，此三品香唯能隨風不能逆風，寧
<lb n="0507b22" ed="T"/>有雅香隨風逆風者乎？」</p><p xml:id="pT02p0507b2210" rend="inline">佛告阿難：「善哉！善哉！
<lb n="0507b23" ed="T"/>誠如汝問，有香真正隨風逆風。」</p><p xml:id="pT02p0507b2313" rend="inline">阿難白佛：「願
<lb n="0507b24" ed="T"/>聞其<note n="0507011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">香＝意【三】</note><note n="0507011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">香＝意【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507011"><lem wit="【大】">香</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">意</rdg></app>。」</p><p xml:id="pT02p0507b2404" rend="inline">佛言：「若於郡國縣邑村落，有善男
<lb n="0507b25" ed="T"/>子善女人，修行十善，身不殺、盜、<note n="0507012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">淫＝婬【三】</note><note n="0507012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">淫＝婬【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507012"><lem wit="【大】">淫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">婬</rdg></app>，口不妄
<lb n="0507b26" ed="T"/>言、兩舌、惡口、綺語，意不嫉<note n="0507013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔妬〕－【三】</note><note n="0507013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔妬〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507013"><lem wit="【大】">妬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>、恚、癡，孝順父
<lb n="0507b27" ed="T"/>母，奉事<note n="0507014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三尊＝三寶【三】</note><note n="0507014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三尊＝三寶【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507014"><lem wit="【大】">三尊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">三寶</rdg></app>，仁慈道德威儀禮節，東方無數
<lb n="0507b28" ed="T"/>沙門梵志歌頌其德，南西北方四維上下沙
<lb n="0507b29" ed="T"/>門梵志咸歌其德：『某郡國土縣邑村落，有善
<pb n="0507c" ed="T" xml:id="T02.0116.0507c"/>
<lb n="0507c01" ed="T"/>男子善女人，<note n="0507015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">奉行十＝及奉行【三】</note><note n="0507015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">奉行十＝及奉行【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507015"><lem wit="【大】">奉行十</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">及奉行</rdg></app>善敬事三寶，孝順仁慈
<lb n="0507c02" ed="T"/>道德恩義不失禮節。』是香名曰隨風逆風靡
<lb n="0507c03" ed="T"/>不周照，十方宣德一切蒙賴。」</p><p xml:id="pT02p0507c0312" rend="inline">佛時頌曰：</p>
<lb n="0507c04" ed="T"/><lg xml:id="lgT02p0507c0401" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「雖有美香花，</l><l>不能逆風熏，</l>
<lb n="0507c05" ed="T"/><l>不息名栴檀，</l><l>眾雨一切香。</l>
<lb n="0507c06" ed="T"/><l>志性能和雅，</l><l>爾乃逆風香，</l>
<lb n="0507c07" ed="T"/><l>正士名丈夫，</l><l>普熏于十方。</l>
<lb n="0507c08" ed="T"/><l>木<note n="0507016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蜜＝櫁【元】【明】</note><app n="0507016"><lem wit="【大】">蜜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">櫁</rdg></app>及栴檀，</l><l>青蓮諸雨香，</l>
<lb n="0507c09" ed="T"/><l>一切此眾香，</l><l>戒香最無上。</l>
<lb n="0507c10" ed="T"/><l>是等清淨<note n="0507017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">者＝戒【三】</note><note n="0507017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">者＝戒【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507017"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">戒</rdg></app>，</l><l>所行無放逸，</l>
<lb n="0507c11" ed="T"/><l>不知魔徑路，</l><l>不見所歸趣。</l>
<lb n="0507c12" ed="T"/><l>此道至永安，</l><l>此道最無上，</l>
<lb n="0507c13" ed="T"/><l>所獲斷穢源，</l><l>降伏絕魔網。</l>
<lb n="0507c14" ed="T"/><l>用上佛道堂，</l><l>昇無窮之慧，</l>
<lb n="0507c15" ed="T"/><l>以此宣<note n="0507018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＝維【三】</note><note n="0507018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經＝維【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507018"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">維</rdg></app>義，</l><l>除去一切弊。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0507c16" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT02p0507c1601">佛告阿難：「是香所布，<note n="0507019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＝無【三】</note><note n="0507019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不＝無【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507019"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">無</rdg></app>礙須彌山川天地，不
<lb n="0507c17" ed="T"/>礙四種地水火風，通達八極上下亦然，無窮
<lb n="0507c18" ed="T"/>之界咸歌其德。一身不殺<note n="0507020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生＝盜媱【三】</note><note n="0507020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">生＝盜媱【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507020"><lem wit="【大】">生</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">盜媱</rdg></app>，世世長壽，其
<lb n="0507c19" ed="T"/>命無<note n="0507021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">橫＝限【三】</note><note n="0507021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">橫＝限【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507021"><lem wit="【大】">橫</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">限</rdg></app>。不盜竊者，世世富饒又不<note n="0507022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">妄＝忘【三】</note><note n="0507022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">妄＝忘【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507022"><lem wit="【大】">妄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">忘</rdg></app>遺財
<lb n="0507c20" ed="T"/>寶常存，施為道根。不<note n="0507023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婬色者＝婬失者【三】</note><note n="0507023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婬色者＝婬失者【宋】【元】【明】，＝婬妷者【磧砂】</note><app n="0507023"><lem wit="【大】">婬色者</lem><rdg resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【磧砂】">婬妷者<note type="cf1">Q18_p0852b04</note></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">婬失者</rdg></app>，<note n="0507024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人〕－【三】</note><note n="0507024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔人〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507024"><lem wit="【大】">人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>不犯<note n="0507025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（他）＋妻【三】</note><note n="0507025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（他）＋妻【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507025"><lem wit="【大】">妻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">他妻</rdg></app>，
<lb n="0507c21" ed="T"/>所在化生蓮華之中。不妄言者，口氣香好言
<lb n="0507c22" ed="T"/><note n="0507026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">輒＝可【三】</note><note n="0507026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">輒＝可【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507026"><lem wit="【大】">輒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">可</rdg></app>信之。不兩舌者，家常和合無<note n="0507027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">有別離＝別離業【三】</note><note n="0507027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有別離＝別離業【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507027"><lem wit="【大】">有別離</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">別離業</rdg></app>。不
<lb n="0507c23" ed="T"/>惡口者，其舌常好言辭辯通。不綺<note n="0507028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">語＝言【三】</note><note n="0507028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">語＝言【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507028"><lem wit="【大】">語</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">言</rdg></app>者，人
<lb n="0507c24" ed="T"/>聞其言莫不諮受宣用為珍。不嫉妬者，世世
<lb n="0507c25" ed="T"/>所生眾人所敬。不瞋恚者，世世端正人見歡
<lb n="0507c26" ed="T"/><note n="0507029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">喜＝然【三】</note><note n="0507029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">喜＝然【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507029"><lem wit="【大】">喜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">然</rdg></app>。除愚癡者，所生智慧靡不諮請，捨于邪
<lb n="0507c27" ed="T"/>見常住正道，從行所得各自然生，故當棄邪
<lb n="0507c28" ed="T"/>從其真妙。」</p><p xml:id="pT02p0507c2805" rend="inline">佛說如是。時，諸比丘聞之歡喜，作
<lb n="0507c29" ed="T"/>禮而去。</p>
<pb n="0508a" ed="T" xml:id="T02.0116.0508a"/>
